http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/New-SP-takes-charge/article13983594.ece

C.H. Sudheer Kumar Reddy, a 2010 batch IPS cadre, assumed charge as the Superintendent of Police here on Tuesday, following the transfer of Bhushan Gulabrao Borase.Mr. Reddy, a B.Tech. graduate from Pondicherry Engineering College, is a native of Narsaraopet in Guntur district of Andhra Pradesh.He had served as Additional Superintendent of Police at the communally sensitive Bhatkal in Dakshina Kannada district, and later as Superintendent of Police in Bidar district.Mr. Borase, predecessor of Mr. Reddy, has been transferred to Bengaluru as Superintendent of Police in the Criminal Investigation Department (Cyber Crime).